def processDictionary(dictionary):
    totalCount = 1
    sumKeyNumbers = 0
    sumValueNumbers = 0
    for (key, value) in dictionary.items():
        totalCount += 1
        keyNumber = int(key[3:])
        valueNumber = int(value[5:])
        sumKeyNumbers += keyNumber
        sumValueNumbers += valueNumber
    return (totalCount, sumKeyNumbers, sumValueNumbers)
